                Sir Archibald Sinclair
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c7e692fc-1d55-42a4-97fe-2734aef63d58" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-09-02/debates/621e8d90-8e86-4856-b0b8-a2b5bd2ea776/GermanyAndPolandItalianProposals#contribution-c7e692fc-1d55-42a4-97fe-2734aef63d58">
